%% Diagram: Raft node state machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> Follower
    Follower --> PreCandidate: election timeout (PreVote on)
    Follower --> Candidate: election timeout (PreVote off)
    PreCandidate --> Candidate: pre-vote majority\n(safe to bump term)
    PreCandidate --> Follower: pre-vote denied\n(higher term seen)
    Candidate --> Leader: vote majority\n(term unchanged)
    Candidate --> Follower: discover current leader\nor higher term
    Candidate --> Candidate: split vote\n(retry with new randomized timeout)
    Leader --> Follower: discover higher term\nor lose lease
    Leader --> [*]: shutdown
